1. how to check syntax
ansible-playbook playbookname.yml --syntax

2. how to dry run playbook
ansible-playbook playbookname.yml --check

3.How to run playbook in verbose mode or see logs
ansible-playbook playbookname.yml -v
ansible-playbook playbookname.yml -vv
ansible-playbook playbookname.yml -vvv

4 How to run task after confirmation only in playbook
ansible-playbook playbookname.yml --step
ansible-playbook playbookname.yml -v --step

5.how to run specific task in playbook or specific task or run some few task


